prodNameC: "銳盟"輪狀病毒乳膠檢測套組(未滅菌)
ingredientsDesc:
1.Test Latex
   One bottle containing a suspension of polystyrene latex particles sensitized with rabbit antibody raised against Nebrasks Calf Diarrhoea rotavirus in buffer with protein stabilizers.
2.Control Latex
   One bottle containing polystyrene latex particles sensitized with non-immune rabbit serum in buffer.
3.Positive Control Antigen
   One bottle containing 0.5 ml of inactivated Nebraska Calf Diarrhoea rotavirus.
4.Extraction buffer
   One bottle containing 25 ml of 0.1 M phosphate buffered 0.85% saline pH 7.3.
applicantName: 成信新貿易股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 新北市中和區中山路二段348巷8號9樓
efficacy: 利用快速乳膠凝集測定檢測人類檢體中的輪狀病毒或其他抗原。
